     H            Y/
     F***************************************************
     F*  RE-ORGANIZE INVENTORY FILE                     *
     F*                                                 *
     F*                                                 *
     F*                                                 *
     F***************************************************
     FAH#PP60 UP  E                    DISK
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140@TIM
     I                                        7  140@YMD
     I                                        7  100@YY
     I                                       11  120@MM
     I                                       13  140@DD
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *------------------------------------------------------
      *  MAIN
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           A6SKDT    IFNE *ZERO
     C           A6SKDT    ANDLT@YMD
     C           A6SHDT    ORNE *ZERO
     C           A6SHDT    ANDLT@YMD
     C                     DELETAH#PP601
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      *------------------------------------------------------
      *  INITIALIZE
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           *INZSR    BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@MM    2
      *
     C                     MOVE P@MM      W@MM    20
     C                     TIME           @TIM
     C           @MM       SUB  W@MM      @MM
     C           @MM       IFLE 0
     C                     ADD  12        @MM
     C                     SUB  1         @YY
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
